    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《Enspell》 的游戏说明</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/e62d21234673aef9eed3b5271d5e1635.poster.avif?t=1707120053\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/e62d21234673aef9eed3b5271d5e1635.webm?t=1707120053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/e62d21234673aef9eed3b5271d5e1635.mp4?t=1707120053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>《Enspell》是一款以中世纪奇幻为题材的卡组养成类游戏，在游戏中，你将揭开秘密，探索宝藏。<br>在危险的地牢中与怪物搏斗时，您可以收集遗物并制作自己的卡组。<br>每次都要用新的卡组建立策略，到达地下城的尽头，也就是最终目标，发现城堡中的秘密！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/7e44bd9f78dbaa1ce33be48c072b585f.poster.avif?t=1707120053\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/7e44bd9f78dbaa1ce33be48c072b585f.webm?t=1707120053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/7e44bd9f78dbaa1ce33be48c072b585f.mp4?t=1707120053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>换卡大战</strong><br>在战斗中更换卡牌，根据情况正确拾取卡牌，并通过更换卡牌使其变得更强。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/ed02fefe67c9d8aff6aa7f018d57fab9.avif?t=1707120053\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>怪物甲板</strong><br>怪物和玩家一样，也会从卡组中抽取卡牌进行战斗。<br>因此，你应该根据怪物选取的牌来考虑本回合要使用哪张牌！<br><br></li><li><strong>继续改变地图</strong><br>每次新玩法的地图结构都会发生变化。<br>选择最适合自己的道路，通过战略性战斗不断成长。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/59f059c9a03eba7c79872316371a3bbb.avif?t=1707120053\" width=600 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏目标</h2>在不同的十字路口，您需要做出明智的选择，将主角带到地牢的最深处。最后，您需要在地牢最深处赢得与敌人的最后一战，这样主角才能实现他的真正目标。<br>祝您好运!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/c1ec664920eedff9a29508c0b8c81cb1.poster.avif?t=1707120053\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/c1ec664920eedff9a29508c0b8c81cb1.webm?t=1707120053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396900/extras/c1ec664920eedff9a29508c0b8c81cb1.mp4?t=1707120053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
